            "fact_heading": "Facts",
            "fact_text": "<p>Accessibility One of the strongest advantages lab grown diamonds have over mined ones is that they’re quick and easy to produce, making them really affordable and accessible. Every mined diamond goes through an extensive process before it reaches your hands. The process includes exploration, extraction, labour-led mining, global transportation, and local distribution before it is finally certified. Every step involved contributes to the high prices which are ultimately paid by the end customer aka you. Even if you compare identical mined and lab grown diamonds, the mined stone will always be more expensive due to the aforementioned added costs. Lab grown diamonds skip quite a lot of expensive steps as they are created in controlled environments and you get to reap the benefits. These diamonds can be created quickly and efficiently, helping bring their costs down. The result? Lab grown diamonds on an average are at least 40 - 70 percent more affordable than mined natural diamonds while offering the same sparkle, brilliance and durability. For you, this means you get to pick a bigger, better gem, bringing your dream diamond within your reach. Indian Jewelry Buyers are price sensitive. We value practical and accessible luxury without compromising on the quality. Lab grown diamonds solve these issues perfectly through advancements in technology, streamlined distribution channels, and protection against global market fluctuations.</p>"
